<HEAD>Adverti&s;ement.</HEAD>
<P>IT is intended, in the pre&s;ent Pub|lication, to collect together the mo&s;t va|luable E&s;&s;ays, Re&s;olutions, Speeches, &amp;c. re&s;pecting the Treaty between the United States and Great Britain.</P>
<P>In the Pro&s;ecution of this Plan, the Publi&s;her pledges him&s;elf to ob&s;erve the &s;tricte&s;t Impartiality, and on this Ob&s;erv|ance re&s;ts his Preten&s;ions to public En|couragement.</P>
