<P>N. B. Tho&s;e per&s;ons to who&s;e names a<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">cri&s;<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">s are placed, were out of town before notice of the meeting was given, and did not attend &s;aid meeting; and of the other &s;ub&s;cribers, it is &s;aid, not more than three or four per&s;ons attended, who totally di&s;approved of the &s;aid proceedings.</P>
